text: Peggy Fleming is an American figure skater and ABC Sports television commentator. She was the champion at 1968 Winter Olympics. She was born July 27, 1948 in San Jose, California. ==References== ==Other websites== Category:1948 births Category:Living people Category:Figure skaters from California Category:Sportspeople from San Jose, California Category:Olympic gold medalists for the United States
